//]]&gt;
</script><script src="https://d15mj6e6qmt1na.cloudfront.net/assets/popup_button.js" type="text/javascript">
</script></center>","type":"text/html"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<p>NOTE: The record button requires that you have Flash installed. If you are trying to record audio on a mobile phone or tablet that doesn&apos;t support Flash, it will prompt you to download the free AudioBoo mobile app first, and use it to record and submit your audio.</p>"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<p><strong>Step Two:</strong> Once have recorded your audio and played it back for review, it&apos;s time to submit it to our editors and producers. Your audio clip will first go into a moderation queue.</p>"},{"content":"<p><strong>UPDATE, 10/18/2013: And we have a winner!</strong> As we wonder whether the government shutdown rattled the Federal Reserve, one anonymous listener rattles at Ben Bernanke. Though we don&apos;t know his name, he says he&apos;s from Flatbush, in Brooklyn -- which coincidentally, is the same New York borough Janet Yellen hails from. Hear his message below, and listen to all of the other contenders <a href="https://audioboo.fm/channel/marketplaceapm" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>","type":"text/html"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<div class="ab-player" data-boourl="https://audioboo.fm/boos/1655893-farewell-to-ben-bernanke-cartoon-challenge-don-t-mess-with-flatbush/embed"><a href="https://audioboo.fm/boos/1655893-farewell-to-ben-bernanke-cartoon-challenge-don-t-mess-with-flatbush">listen to ‘Farewell to Ben Bernanke Cartoon Challenge: Don&apos;t Mess with Flatbush.....’ on Audioboo</a></div>"},{"content":"<script type="text/javascript">
